{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC03_JUL_220.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x20,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Sophie, perfect timing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ah, Sir Julio."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "I received a letter from Nazarus."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "From Nazarus?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Yes, it appears he reached the next town. He visited the church there."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "He said they're taking good care of him, and he wanted to thank me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I see, that's good."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "He also sent a package with the letter. He wanted you to have it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Wait, it's for me?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x44,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Yes, he addressed it to you. Will you take it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Thank you, I will."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "I'd like to thank you again, Sophie. If it wasn't for you, I wouldn't have been able to save Nazarus."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "I'm glad I met you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "No way, it's all because of your hard work."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "No. You made the medicine, and if it wasn't for your words, I would have lost heart and never seen it through."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "And you also helped me realize something important."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Huh?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I always talk about how a knight must protect everyone, but there's a limit to what I can accomplish alone."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Because of that, I never wanted to stay in one place for long. I became a knight of the Church, rather than a country."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "My feelings never changed as a result. But your words helped me realize something."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "My words?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Yes, you told me something before we delivered the medicine to Nazarus."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "You said that other people would be sad if I killed Nazarus."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Protecting people in front of my eyes indirectly leads to bringing happiness to others unseen."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x19,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "There's no need to do something grand for the sake of all. Protecting the people I see now is more than enough."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2f,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I see... I think you're right about that, Sir Julio."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x4,
            "name_id": 0x4,
            "extra_id": 0x42,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "So thank you, Sophie. I look forward to our continued endeavors."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, me too!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "(Helping the people you see now, huh... Alchemy might be the same way.)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x32,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "(Alright, I'll work even harder at alchemy!)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Received \"<CLGR>Forgotten Ore<CLNR>\"."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Julio learned the skill \"<CLGR>Paladin's Soul<CLNR>\"."
        }
    ]
}